title: Tom Petty&TheHeartbreakers_ABunchOfVideosAndSomeOtherStuff
description:
Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers in a blatant example of crass commercialism, seem to believe that great music and award winning visuals and never-before-seen comic vignettes are all it takes to dupe the public into acquiring this compilation of their classic videos. Well...maybe they're right!
